landing.login-section.title: Localization made simple
landing.login-section.subtitle: Localize Web and Native Apps incredibly easy with Linguallo. Simple, scalable and free localization management and localization delivery solution.
landing.content-section.title: Translate your content by using our user-friendly and coherent spreadsheets
landing.content-section.subtitle: Linguallo's spreadsheets offer endless possibilities both to organizations and developers and to translators.
landing.hero-section.title: Using Linguallo cuts localization time in half
landing.hero-section.subtitle: No more time consuming manual copy/paste actions. Linguallo's easy-to-use spreadsheets and powerful publisher help you change your translations fast for automatically visible results on your Website and Apps.
landing.flow-section.title: Linguallo lets you work more collaboratively and get more done.
landing.flow-section.subtitle: Linguallo's spreadsheets and sheets enable you to organize your translations in a flexible way.
landing.get-started-section.title: Start Localizing Today
landing.get-started-section.subtitle: Make the most of localization by signing up for Linguallo to get more done.
landing.feature-section.publisher.title: Linguallo supports many of localization file formats across platforms and programming languages
landing.feature-section.publisher.subtit: Importing and exporting from XLIFF and CSV has never been easier. Linguallo's publisher delivers translation files to your Web or Native Apps in different formats such as .json, .xml, .strings and many more.
